@startuml
!theme amiga
title amiga Theme Showcase
Alice -> Bob: hello
Bob -> Charlie: forward
Charlie --> Bob: ack
Bob --> Alice: done
alt success
  Alice -> Alice: log success
else error
  Alice -> Alice: log error
end
@enduml

